    <date month="April" year="2015"></date>
    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document proposes a new ICMP message that a router or host may use to advise a host to reduce the rate at which it sends, in cases where the host ignores other signals provided by packet loss and Explicit Congestion Notification (ECN).&lt;/p&gt;</t>
